id: pm-b8rf
title: "Expose agent guidance init option in settings, contracts, help, and config"
description: "Make the new pm init agent-guidance behavior discoverable and machine-safe across settings schema/types, runtime help, SDK contracts, MCP action schema, and optional config inspection."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
