acceptance_criteria: settings schema accepts and persists agent_guidance deterministically; pm init help and JSON help include the guidance option; pm contracts --command init --flags-only and action schema expose the option; MCP schema can pass the option; config/docs give a clear operator path to inspect or reset declined state if implemented.
