  "2026-05-17T08:59:44.986Z",codex-agent,Child task created from pm-7t04. This slice makes the UX contract visible to humans and agents after prompt behavior exists.
  "2026-05-17T10:10:15.712Z",codex-agent,"Added agent_guidance state to settings defaults/schema/serialization and wired init option visibility through runtime contracts, help text, and shell completion outputs for agent-safe discoverability."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-17T10:10:17.427Z",codex-agent,Contract and completion updates keep MCP/tool payloads in sync with CLI option parsing so agents can rely on --agent-guidance in both shell and tool-driven flows.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-17T10:10:19.053Z",codex-agent,"When introducing new init flags, update SDK contracts first and derive completion/help surfaces from those contracts to minimize drift."
